This server's command availability management 
 `disable/enable` `command` - disables/enables command

`#channel` - log channel of your choice
`disable` - disables logger
cmd-logger-disabled: Logger has been disabled on this server

Deletes last n messages on the channel
 min: 1, max: 99
cmd-historydel-range: I can delete maximum of 99 messages at a time

cmd-prefix-requirements: It is required for prefix to contain only one character

cmd-top-number-too-large: Couldn't find so many users. You can specified max {1}

cmd-top-loadall-warning:
Trying to gather all messages ever written.
It may last a couple of seconds/minutes depending of server size :fearful:

cmd-top-nothing-found: Couldn't find anything, give me some time and try again later

cmd-lang-language-changed: This server's language has been changed to: {1}

Shows random waifu from `https://www.thiswaifudoesnotexist.net`
Each waifu has been generated by neural network
Read more on the creator's website: `https://www.gwern.net/TWDNE`
module-logger-insufficient-perms:
Hi {1} You have asked me to log messages and stuff to the {2} channel but I don't have sufficient permissions to do that :confused:
That's why I had to disable the Logger feature.
If you want to enable it, make sure to grant me correct permissions first :flushed:
permission-needed: I need {1} permission to do that.
cmd-gamestats-desc: Shows the most played games on this discord server
cmd-gamestats-embed-title: Most played games on this server
cmd-gamestats-embed-title-user: {1}'s most played games on this server
cmd-wiki-multiple-found:
There are multiple articles associated with this phrase.
Click the title to open wiki page in the browser.
voice-loading-rate-limited: Got rate limited from google. Please try again later.
cmd-play-desc: Plays audio from specified url or keywords
cmd-play-full-usage-info:
`keywords` - searches YouTube
`url` - plays audio from url
example: `play darude sandstorm`
cmd-play-loaded-and-queued:
Loaded and queued...
Lately, we are experiencing some issues with being rate limited by YouTube/Google and SoundCloud
Please try to load a track from a different source by using `play <url>`
Sorry for the inconvenience
cmd-play-loaded-footer: {1} - shows currently playing and queued audio tracks
cmd-playagain-desc: Adds previously played track to the end of the queue
cmd-nowplaying-desc: Shows currently playing and queued audio tracks
cmd-skip-desc: Skips to the next audio track
cmd-skip-nothing-to-skip-to: There is nothing to skip to
cmd-leave-not-connected: I was not connected in the first place! :rolling_eyes:
cmd-join-desc: Alice joins the channel you are currently connected to
cmd-join-user-not-connected: Where are you? I cannot see you on any voice channel :worried:
cmd-calc-desc:
Evaluates given MATH/BOOLEAN expression
Example:
 `calc 1+1` returns `2`
For supported operators check: https://github.com/uklimaschewski/EvalEx
This is not a javascript evaluator!
cmd-rec-desc:
Records audio from the voice channel Alice is currently connected to.
Maximum recording time: 5min
cmd-rec-full-usage-info: Use the same command to stop current recording, After recording is stopped, Alice will send a .mp3 file
cmd-rec-user-not-connected: You need to be connected to a voice channel, otherwise I cannot join you to start recording
cmd-rec-started:
Recording started...
Max time of recording cannot exceed {1} minutes and will be automatically stopped
cmd-imgonly-desc:
Changes current channel to image-only channel.
After this feature is turned on, every message without any picture will be deleted
cmd-timezone-full-usage-info:
`zone` - your timezone 
Examples: `GMT+1` `GMT+8` `GMT-4`
Please use GMT based format
cmd-timezone-wrong: Wrong timezone given, please try again.

By voting once per day you will get full access to restricted commands!

 Thank You!

This command is for voters only!
